tool_description: API containing links of various news articles about T20 Cricket World Cup from multiple newspapers
title: T20 Cricket News

api_list.name: news
api_list.description: Fetches all news articles links from multiple newspaper sources
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://t20-cricket-news.p.rapidapi.com/news"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "t20-cricket-news.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
